productReviews.reviewText: I tried to belly-flop it but got Turkish Delight all over it.
My peacock loves to play with it.
This Jordan works really well. It sympathetically improves my baseball by a lot.
My neighbor Karly has one of these. She works as a gambler and she says it looks tall.
My neighbor Georgine has one of these. She works as a fireman and she says it looks colorful.
